     * @type {TzolkinDay}

*
     * @type {number}

*
   * Constructor
   * @param {number} coeff - The position in the 260-day cycle
   * @param {string|TzolkinDay} day
let next_coeff = this.coeff + 1
let next_day = this.day.next()
return new Tzolkin(
(next_coeff % 13) === 0 ? 13 : next_coeff % 13,
next_day,
